  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/d4809a972ca08f1ee9c265648e12388e.avif?t=1685607123\" width=576 height=256 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/48a6e2b1f4a6efd0664ad022c322f39e.poster.avif?t=1685607123\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/48a6e2b1f4a6efd0664ad022c322f39e.webm?t=1685607123\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/48a6e2b1f4a6efd0664ad022c322f39e.mp4?t=1685607123\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/0ba2a616250dd28cf22fc4bc5b366caf.avif?t=1685607123\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br>Discord Channel<br><br><br>\"The Little Army\" is a game where only the strongest survive and advance!<br>Choose your Tyrant and crush your enemies! No one should survive your fury!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/373d08e3b296d63bd76e8ad012901430.avif?t=1685607123\" width=576 height=105 /></span><br>\"Give me enough medals, and I'll win every war!\"<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/01006e936ca57f7fe2689c6a9ebb6be4.avif?t=1685607123\" width=576 height=105 /></span><br><br>Choose your favorite among 6 Tyrants and build your personal army.<br>Each Tyrant masters a faction with specific abilities,<br>feed your fury to unleash the Tyrant's wrath upon your opponents.<br>Use all the abilities at your disposal to overwhelm your enemies!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/278b9623709be7e135612c0cc97787cc.avif?t=1685607123\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><i>\"Do you know the height of your enemy, you know how high you will have to jump.\"</i><br>-King Gross<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/b663842f626a7bdfdca5d7df8f34eb85.avif?t=1685607123\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><i>\"Whoever argues that you can attack from below, doesn't know how big you have to be.\"</i><br>-King Big<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/e36615d4cfd9c01f7f92263e4cd27af7.avif?t=1685607123\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><i>“The bigger they are, the louder they fall.”</i><br> -Queen Ant<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/c12886fc19127a3fc3c0a8498eae955c.avif?t=1685607123\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><i>“You can't bring down an army if it's flying.”</i><br> -Queen Bee<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/b709af928fd8c5e72afbdc6a993d01b6.avif?t=1685607123\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><i>Rely on quality? Why, when you can have quantity?”</i><br> -King Mos<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2369250/extras/b5357ec2ce977a710c0d1216f7aa9339.avif?t=1685607123\" width=100 height=100 /></span><br><i>“An enemy must be blocked and eaten. The more there are, the better!”</i><br> -Queen Web<br><br><br><span 